                    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"><article class="caaft-ar-offer-card"><span class="caaft-ar-offer-num">01</span><h3 class="caaft-ar-offer-card-title">Monthly MIS Reporting</h3><p class="caaft-ar-offer-card-text">Consistent monthly financial updates that help businesses track performance and monitor key financial metrics — including revenue and sales performance summaries, expense tracking and cost breakdowns, profitability analysis, budget vs actual comparisons, and cash flow analysis reports. Regular MIS reports ensure business owners and directors always have access to accurate financial information — enabling early identification of trends and timely corrective action when needed.</p></article></div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"><article class="caaft-ar-offer-card"><span class="caaft-ar-offer-num">02</span><h3 class="caaft-ar-offer-card-title">Financial Performance Analysis</h3><p class="caaft-ar-offer-card-text">In-depth evaluation of how effectively a business generates revenue and manages expenses — analysing profit and loss statements, balance sheets, and cash flow statements to assess revenue growth, cost structure, profit margins, expense optimisation, and operational efficiency. Particularly valuable for companies planning expansion, seeking investment, or looking to improve financial performance across the business.</p></article></div>
