                    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"><article class="caaft-ar-offer-card"><span class="caaft-ar-offer-num">04</span><h3 class="caaft-ar-offer-card-title">Profitability Analysis</h3><p class="caaft-ar-offer-card-text">Evaluation of which products, services, or business units contribute the most value — identifying where costs can be reduced and processes optimised to improve overall profit margins and financial performance.</p></article></div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"><article class="caaft-ar-offer-card"><span class="caaft-ar-offer-num">05</span><h3 class="caaft-ar-offer-card-title">Budget vs Actual Reporting</h3><p class="caaft-ar-offer-card-text">Regular comparison of actual financial results against planned budgets — highlighting variances, identifying performance gaps, and providing the data needed to make timely adjustments to business strategy.</p></article></div>
